summary: If a Spinarak finds the web of another Spinarak in its range it will eat it and leave the other Spinarak without a trap to catch...
body: If a Spinarak finds the web of another Spinarak in its range it will eat it and leave the other Spinarak without a trap to catch prey. This way it gets a free meal and doesn’t have to worry about others catching pokemon that it would otherwise catch.
